iltonian for any pulsed experiment. The\nformalism has been applied to understand established dipolar recoupling pulse\nsequences. Limitations of the pulse sequences are addressed by designing novel\nvariants of the pulse sequences, aided by insights gained through the effective\nHamiltonian description.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Nov 2017 19:22:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-21"}
